source.name: DOJ Litigation Outcomes Fiscal Year 2010
source.description: The annual data tables contained in this document provide summary statistics on the civil enforcement activities of the United States Trustee Program.  These tables summarize data for Fiscal Year 2004 through Fiscal Year 2010 (October 1, 2003 through September 30, 2010).  This report covers litigation outcomes.  Successful Litigation Outcomes include outcomes where the court entered an order granting the relief sought by the United States Trustee, in whole or in part, or the defendant agreed to other relief satisfactory to the United States Trustee.
